before we start, a quick note about census geographies

...OK let's go! Census 2021 data for england and wales is out now¶

  • I work for the part of London that has the fastest growing, most densely populated, most young and least old population: Tower Hamlets
  • in the course of trying to map some of these phenomena i ended publishing a data vis package in python called data mountains

made with #nbdev!¶

using nbdev for this project made it extra fun, it helps you show good coder practice¶

  1. it cleans cell metadata during version control, avoiding merge conflicts
  2. it enables you to easily share:
    1. code
    2. docs
    3. tests
    4. modules ... all at once!
